<span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，因此它的概率应该是所有有限并集的上界。类似地，一个<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>句子应该被视为可数交集，其概率被视为下确界。这在概率论中很好，但我的意思是，“上确界”和“下确界”不是可计算函数，您需要引出无限数量的赌注。</p><blockquote><p><i>事实上，考虑无限事件的愿望基本上是在概率论中使用西格玛代数而不是集合代数的动机。</i>集合代数对应于命题逻辑；西格玛代数到谓词逻辑（当然，是<i>二阶</i>逻辑而不是一阶逻辑，因为您可以采用任何可数的并集和交集，甚至不一定以可计算的方式枚举，这对应于某些超算术理论）。</p></blockquote><p>实际上<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （可验证）和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （可证伪）句子仍然可以：对于可验证句子，只要/当句子被验证时向交易者付款即可；对于可伪造的句子，交易者将预先支付 1 美元，如果句子被伪造，则将其返还。这些分别是我们所说的“多头”和“空头”头寸。</p><p>所以哲学家会告诉你除了<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>之外没有任何东西，但他们肯定是错的吗？因为我们实际上可能关心“素数有无限多个”和“所有人都会死”这样的句子。我们<i>可能关心它们</i>，意味着我们的效用函数可能依赖于它们。我们只需要构建一种情况，其中效用函数完全依赖于这样的句子而不是其他任何东西，即设计一个评分规则来得出此类句子的概率。</p><hr><h2><strong>替代介绍：逻辑句子的理论独立定价</strong></h2><p>从表面上看，加拉布兰特归纳似乎是逻辑不确定性的完全自然的形式主义，没有特殊的技巧——<i>当然，</i>市场是处理算法不确定性的正确方法（它们是“聚合算法信息”的自然方法，因为它们汇总所有交易者的信息，包括算法信息），<i>当然</i>您需要一个不可利用性/荷兰书标准。</p><p>但实际上，Garrabrant 归纳法不仅仅是“市场”——它还有几个额外的结构：</p><ul><li>实际上，你不可能只为所有逻辑句子建立一个预测市场，因为它并不像所有数学主张的基本事实在某个时刻都得到明确揭示。我什至不是在谈论无法证明的句子——即使是“素数有无限多个”这句话也<i>既不可验证也不可证伪</i>！<i>皮亚诺算术</i>相信这一点，而加拉布兰特归纳法所做的就是在 PA 证明这一点时还清判决。</li><li>但加拉布兰特归纳法<i>也不</i>是“ <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathsf{PA}\vdash \phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-sans-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-sans-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊢</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">phi</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ”的预测市场——它实际上试图为不可判定的句子分配一个价格。这是因为整个“命题一致的世界”技巧，具体来说：做市商总是愿意<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi+\lnot\phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">将</span></span><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">ψ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ψ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>换成<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="$1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">美元</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，即使<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\phi"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">ψ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>独立于<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathsf{PA}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-sans-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-sans-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</li><li>对本文来说不太重要，但值得一提：它只主导连续交易者；它还有一种奇怪的计算平衡的方式，而像 LMSR 这样的东西会更好。</li></ul><p>总的来说，我认为市场完全依赖形式理论作为真理来源是不能令人满意的——这使得很难在纯数学领域之外进行概括，你不能用它来设计好的代理，而且我认为逻辑不确定性的完整理论应该同时解决<i>“为什么首先要相信逻辑”的问题？</i> ，答案应该看起来像“因为逻辑在市场上赚了很多钱”。</p><hr><h2><strong>问题并非微不足道</strong></h2><p>一个明显的、直接的解决方案可能看起来像归纳结构，其中对于<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>句子，您可以在第<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>天向交易者提供资产<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bigvee_{x\le n}P(x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋁</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">≤</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，在第二天将其收回，无限循环，因此资产价值在无限时间内接近<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_{n+1}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>资产<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\exists x,P(x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∃</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p>但这实际上行不通。我们可以用算术句子的简单图形描述来说明这一点 - 例如，一个<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>句子可以表述为： 考虑一个由白色和黑色方块组成的无限网格。它有一排完全由黑色方块组成的吗？ </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:49.42%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/hcpk3ntfftpzdmzhcobd" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/qtepnyaap9x3o9ijcvrn 100w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/tdsyviccbyrwkynd0nry 200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/zdndfumb35lqrhxs07on 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/g2iw7o7hhetdepsdmry1 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/rlgggmw44u2vkfo5cem1 500w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/mn9ec4g6aok0kvn4m7pq 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/iezypqouqxma8qsaxrah 700w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/lwpbba2v3iayzmgetosw 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/wdp4c2tf7yzrzc2u2ooz 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/nkcgetxngzn4dyqbjs8y 920w"></figure><p>那么所描述的评分机制就相当于每天看棋盘上的有限块，如果有全黑的行就给他 1 美元；第二天，您扩展该块，收回前一天的所有奖励并重复练习。本质上，我们用序列<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bigvee_{x\le n}\bigwedge_{y\le n}P(x,y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋁</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">≤</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-munderover MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋀</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; 